---

Data Privacy Notice:

This bot processes:
- Telegram user IDs and usernames (for access control)
- Movie file names (for parsing and TMDB searches)
- TMDB movie metadata (temporarily cached)

The bot does NOT:
- Store movie files
- Collect personal user data
- Share data with third parties
- Track user activity beyond basic logging